<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: 【Medium quality】Spiritual root -->
  <EnergyRoot.label>【中品】灵芽</EnergyRoot.label>
  <!-- EN: A Medium quality Spiritual root stored in a copper box, requiring refrigeration.\n\nA Spiritual Root is a benign neurotumor, about the size of a mung bean, located within the prefrontal cortex. Those who possess a Spiritual Root can perceive the presence of Qi energy in the atmosphere and absorb it for Cultivation.\n\nBased on its activity level, a Spiritual Root is classified into three grades: low, medium, and best. The higher the grade, the more efficient the absorption of Qi energy.\n\nMedium quality Spiritual root – Qi energy absorption efficiency ×100%. -->
  <EnergyRoot.description>一颗装在铜匣内的中品灵芽，需要冷藏保存。\n\n灵芽是一颗绿豆大小的良性神经瘤，位于前额叶内部。拥有灵芽之人，可感受到大气中灵气的存在，吸收灵气进行修炼。\n\n灵芽按照其活跃性，分为上中下三个品级，品级越高，灵气增长效率也越高。\n\n中品灵芽-灵气增长效率x100%</EnergyRoot.description>
  <!-- EN: Inject Spiritual root to become a cultivator -->
  <EnergyRoot.comps.CompUsableRoot.useLabel>植入灵芽，变成修炼者</EnergyRoot.comps.CompUsableRoot.useLabel>
  
